{"tid":1800880,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"簡單ac/dc conversion問題","createTime":"2019-12-28T08:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T09:44:05.000Z","uid":90633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"37aeffae74d8b7c968607547bc929cf36d1f3c93","tid":1800880,"uid":90633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T08:46:00.000Z","msg":"借AC post<br />\n小弟最近自學緊powerE<br />\n想design 一個ac轉dc (Vout: 24V, 200mA)<br />\nQ1. 唔知點解過到diode出唔到24V, 好似淨係出到12V (未加filtering cap 同埋兩隻diode扣左1.9V<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n同埋current好似都差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ncheck過scope(XSC1) secondary voltage output waveform係24Vrms冇錯<br />\nQ2. 另外想請教下我係咪diode揀錯左 下面有datasheet (同埋想問下diode應該要點揀? 我係睇Vrrm, Vr有冇大過secondary voltage, 上網搵好少教揀diode<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1N4002G datasheet:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v3tnfn3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv3tnfn3.jpg&h=9b54b0e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ncircuit: <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JaHCOGn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJaHCOGn.jpg&h=7cb3a4e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffcf6125e2a67d42bd53b626a571651e19c0e5f4","tid":1800880,"uid":90633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T08:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbdf0552e70098a9a6ae535401d3bbb79e92605c","tid":1800880,"uid":9769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T09:14:19.000Z","msg":"去深水埗買隻牛會唔會簡單D？"},{"pid":"570edd9819381dc60d855c762f7ff87d2def56c1","tid":1800880,"uid":70117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T09:24:26.000Z","msg":"要55:6:6"},{"pid":"4d1579075ca8484429910033b203d47c60da835c","tid":1800880,"uid":173951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T09:37:26.000Z","msg":"似係Secondary Side圈數錯左<br />\n電壓同線圈數係Linear成正比<br />\n<br />\n樓主呢個火牛Secondary Side有兩組線圈<br />\n兩組Secondary Side都係3圈<br />\nPrimary Side 55圈<br />\n55/3 = 18<br />\n220 / 18 = 12.22V<br />\n所以對地度度出黎係12V<br />\n<br />\n利伸： 電子底差 嘗試解而已..."},{"pid":"b5fd9b5a387b427a2e684e9da4ac5239bd1e2a03","tid":1800880,"uid":95630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T09:37:37.000Z","msg":"係你依家個setting<br />\n<br />\nstep down咗個peak to peak Ac voltage 去 12V<br />\n<br />\n過埋diode就會變咗做6V DC voltage<br />\n<br />\n如果你想有12V voltage<br />\n<br />\n你係要有一個 target Dc voltage 2倍嘅 step down peak to peak Ac voltage"},{"pid":"87736e050dfb40933714fb8cb523c7ef4fcd1888","tid":1800880,"uid":95630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5fd9b5a387b427a2e684e9da4ac5239bd1e2a03","tid":1800880,"uid":95630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T09:37:37.000Z","msg":"係你依家個setting<br />\n<br />\nstep down咗個peak to peak Ac voltage 去 12V<br />\n<br />\n過埋diode就會變咗做6V DC voltage<br />\n<br />\n如果你想有12V voltage<br />\n<br />\n你係要有一個 target Dc voltage 2倍嘅 step down peak to peak Ac voltage"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T09:44:05.000Z","msg":"個Vrms要係48V先啱<br />\n<br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}